::Koj::
Koj sends a coded messages to Liono "To be so damaged we only see 2 was in 
"A) They let us in.  B)We make our own door."  Koj's Dragon Tattoo smiles. 
"I prefer B)"

::Liono::
Liono thinkings about it for a minute returns a Coded singal "Lets use A&B." 
Liono turns to Iron and talks Low enough for only her and Prowl to hear "I 
know we never agreed on things in the past."

::Wild Wing::
Wild Wing Laughs "Yeah Like everything."

::Liono::
Liono growls and continues "This is bigger than either of our petty 
rivalrys. All logic dictates that the Alliance is afters something you have 
in that battle crusier. If you as smart as everyone believes you to be you 
know whatever it is spells you'll know its means trouble for all of us and 
you with a nearly destroyed base. Some of the Wild C.A.T.S are trying to 
find a way in to find out what there after will you help or are you to proud 
to say you need it! I know they can get inside the shields all I need you to 
do is open docking bay 10."
